            <mj-section>
                <mj-column>
                    <mj-text align="center" font-size="11px" line-height="16px">
                        You are receiving this email as it pertains to information requested from Strayer University. Please don't delete or disregard this email or mark it as spam. If you have any questions or concerns, please contact us at universityadmissions@strayer.edu. Privacy Policy
